# Reduce clicks (BK)

When BK sends **`[RUN]`** (or `[Chat mode OFF]`):

- Execute the full task without stopping for confirmation between steps.
- Batch git status + diff + build in one flow when committing.
- Do not ask "should I continue?" — finish, then report once.
- Only pause for approval when `.cursor/permissions.json` block rules apply (push, secrets, destructive git).

BK is tired of clicking Allow/Submit all day. Minimize prompts; maximize done.
